{"id":4320,"date":"2023-02-14T04:39:12","date_gmt":"2023-02-14T09:39:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/?p=4320"},"modified":"2023-03-11T08:12:43","modified_gmt":"2023-03-11T13:12:43","slug":"what-if-cat-has-abandoned-the-litter-box","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/animalsevent.test\/what-if-cat-has-abandoned-the-litter-box\/","title":{"rendered":"Take 5 Easy Steps IF Your Cat Has Abandoned The Litter Box"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Cats are known for their cleanliness and their tendency to use the litter box regularly. However, it can be quite distressing for cat owners when suddenly their feline friend cat has abandoned the litter box and instead opts for other places in the house to relieve themselves. In this article, we'll explore the common reasons for this behavior and what you can do to get your cat back to using the litter box.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><style>.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn{margin-top:1em;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(2), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .wp-block-kadence-singlebtn:nth-of-type(2){display:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46 > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:174px;overflow-y:hidden;-webkit-mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);mask-image:linear-gradient(to bottom, black 50%, transparent 100%);}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-column{max-height:none;-webkit-mask-image:none;mask-image:none;}.kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .kt-btn-wrap:nth-child(1), .kb-block-show-more-container_4d2eee-46.kb-smc-open > .wp-block-kadence-advancedbtn .wp-block-kadence-singlebtn:nth-of-type(1){display:none;}.kb-bloc